OL,3,CPolice given extended powers after car
OL,4,Cchase and machetes
OL,6,FPolice have been given extended stop
OL,7,Fand search powers after a number
OL,8,Fincidents involving machetes and a car
OL,9,Fchase.
OL,11,FThe disorder broke out in Oldham on
OL,12,Fthe evening of Thursday 03 July, with
OL,13,Fpolice first being called to Lee
OL,14,FStreet after receiving reports of a
OL,15,Fchase between two SUVs.
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police said two men
OL,18,Fin their 20s and a man in his 50s have
OL,19,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of affray
OL,20,Fand remain in custody for questioning.
