OL,3,CPolice given extended powers after car
OL,4,Cchase and machetes
OL,6,FThe force authorised Section 60 powers
OL,7,Fto run from 2.59am on Friday until the
OL,8,Fsame time on Saturday under the
OL,9,FCriminal Justice and Public Order Act
OL,10,F1994.
OL,12,FOne of the two SUVs collided with a
OL,13,Ftree before men with machetes who were
OL,14,Fchasing the vehicle attempted to
OL,15,Fattack the driver, GMP said.
OL,17,FAt about 10.20pm another disturbance
OL,18,Finvolving at least 10 men "with
OL,19,Fvarious weapons" was reported, the
OL,20,Fforce added.
