OL,4,Cchase and machetes
OL,6,FPolice said they found more than 100
OL,7,Fpeople were on the street, "with
OL,8,Fpockets of disorder still in the area"
OL,9,Fthat dispersed after officers arrived.
OL,11,FAround 15 minutes later officers
OL,12,Fresponded to claims a man had been
OL,13,Fattacked on Roundthorn Road, and found
OL,14,Fa "smashed taxi" and a man in his 20s
OL,15,Fwith minor injuries.
