OL,3,CPolice given extended powers after car
OL,4,Cchase and machetes
OL,6,FSuperintendent Cara Charlesworth, from
OL,7,FGMP's Oldham division, said: "Our
OL,8,Fnumber one priority, as always, is
OL,9,Fkeeping the community in Oldham safe,
OL,10,Fand I believe this Section 60
OL,11,Fauthority is proportionate and
OL,12,Fnecessary following a number of
OL,13,Fincidents overnight.
OL,15,F"This authority enables officers to
OL,16,Futilise extra powers to stop-search
OL,17,Findividuals and hopefully ensure some
OL,18,Fpotentially dangerous weapons that we
OL,19,Fhave been aware of overnight, are
OL,20,Ftaken off the streets.
