OL,3,CPolice given extended powers after car
OL,4,Cchase and machetes
OL,6,F"We have made arrests, seized vehicles
OL,7,Fthat are believed to be involved in
OL,8,Fthese incidents, CCTV inquires are
OL,9,Fongoing and arrest attempts for
OL,10,Foutstanding suspects are being made."
OL,12,FShe added: "I would like to reassure
OL,13,Fthe public that we are putting extra
OL,14,Fresources into the area to provide
OL,15,Freassurance, which will continue into
OL,16,Fthis evening and throughout the
OL,17,Fweekend.
