OL,6,F"If you see any of our officers out on
OL,7,Fpatrol, please speak to us, we are
OL,8,Flooking for any information that would
OL,9,Fassist us with our inquiries and your
OL,10,Fsupport is vital."
OL,12,FThe Section 60 order covers the
OL,13,Fjunction between Constantine Street
OL,14,Fand Greenacres Road, Greenacres Road
OL,15,Fto Oldham Way, and Oldham Way to Park
OL,16,FRoad.
